# This file IS the supported / mirrored set — the air-gap-authoritative answer to
# "which OCP versions can a cluster actually be here, so CAPA must have a matching
# aliyun boot image". It is committed, so the CI runner (which has NO local
# ansible/group_vars/all.yml) has an explicit, auditable source decoupled from the
# operator's local all.yml.
